Block,Chain,Roulette,is,a,Bitcoin,game,that,rewards,users,who,correctly,guess,a,random,number,that,is,generated,by,solving,a,new,Bitcoin,block,The,Block,Chain,Roulette,API,gives,users,access,to,URLS,to,enable,them,to,create,their,own,roulette,playing,bots,The,API,has,queries,that,can,get,a,list,of,all,possible,bets,get,a,list,of,all,bests,made,on,the,table,get,a,list,of,the,last,bets,and,get,a,list,of,blocks,processed,and,spin,results